;; ** What is ivy-posframe

;; ivy-posframe is a ivy extension, which let ivy use posframe to show
;; its candidate menu.

;; NOTE: ivy-posframe requires Emacs 26 and do not support mouse
;; click.

;; ** Display functions

;; 1. ivy-posframe-display
